config BR2_PACKAGE_GDAL
	bool "GDAL"
        select BR2_PACKAGE_JPEG
        select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBPNG
        select BR2_PACKAGE_TIFF
        select BR2_PACKAGE_ZLIB
	help
          GDAL is a translator library for raster and vector
          geospatial data formats that is released under an X/MIT
          style Open Source license by the Open Source Geospatial
          Foundation. As a library, it presents a single raster
          abstract data model and single vector abstract data model to
          the calling application for all supported formats. It also
          comes with a variety of useful command line utilities for
          data translation and processing.

	  http://www.gdal.org/
